Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,one two three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,undead tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:26.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I’ll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:37.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I see that bright light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:43.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,this is all I have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what did you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:53.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,why do you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,刃を砥ぐ、微睡む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:01.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:05.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,詩と快楽は未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:13.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:16.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,final white heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,さあ奪い合うよ傷を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:22.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:28.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:26.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我將成為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:37.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:43.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,這就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:53.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你為什麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,磨刀 小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:01.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,生存之景
